    • getNeighbour

      public Space getNeighbour​(@NotNull @NotNull Space space, @NotNull @NotNull Heading heading)
      Returns the neighbour of the given space of the board in the given heading. The neighbour is returned only, if it can be reached from the given space (no walls or obstacles in either of the involved spaces); otherwise, null will be returned.
      Parameters:
      space - the space for which the neighbour should be computed
      heading - the heading of the neighbour
      Returns:
      the space in the given direction; null if there is no (reachable) neighbour
